quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  46,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  46,1,h m
  46,2,iss kitaab ka nuzool Allah zabardast aur Dana ki taraf se hai
  46,3,"hum ne zameen aur asmano ko aur unn saari cheezon ko jo unn ke darmain hain brhq, aur aik muddat khaas ke taayun ke sath peda kya hai magar yeh kafir log uss haqeeqat se mun moray hue hain jis se un ko khabardaar kya gaya hai"
  46,4,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho,"" kabhi tum ne ankhen khol kar dekha bhi ke woh hastiyan hain kya jinhein tum khuda ko chore kar pkarte ho? zara mujhe dikhao to sahi ke zameen mein unhon ne kya peda kya hai, ya asmano ki takhleeq o tadbeer mein un ka kya hissa hai iss se pehlay aayi hui kitaab ya ilm ka koi baqiya ( inn aqaed ke saboot mein ) tumahray paas ho to wohi le aao agar tum sachey ho """
  46,5,aakhir uss shakhs se ziyada b_hka howa ensaan aur kon ho ga jo Allah ko chore kar unn ko pukare jo qayamat taq usay jawab nahi day satke balkay iss se bhi be khabar hain ke pukarnay walay unn ko pukaar rahay hain
  46,6,aur jab tamam ensaan jama kiye jayen ge uss waqt woh apne pukarnay walon ke dushman aur un ki ibadat ke munkir hon ge
  46,7,inn logon ko jab hamari saaf saaf ayaat sunai jati hain aur haq inn ke samnay aa jata hai to yeh kafir log uss ke mutaliq kehte hain ke yeh to khula jaadoo hai
  46,8,"kya unn ka kehna yeh hai ke rasool ne isay khud ghurr liya hai? un se kaho,"" agar mein ne isay khud ghurr liya hai to tum mujhe khuda ki pakar se kuch bhi nah bacha sakuu ge, jo baatein tum banatay ho Allah un ko khoob jaanta hai, mere aur tumahray darmain wohi gawahi dainay ke liye kaafi hai, aur woh bara dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai """
  46,9,"inn se kaho,"" mein koi nirala rasool to nahi hon, mein nahi jaanta ke kal tumahray sath kya hona hai aur mere sath kya, mein to sirf uss wahi ki pairwi karta hon jo mere paas bhaije jati hai aur mein aik saaf saaf khabardaar kar dainay walay ke siwa aur kuch nahi hon """
  46,10,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho"" kabhi tum ne socha bhi ke agar yeh kalaam Allah hi ki taraf se howa aur tum ne iss ka inkaar kar diya ( to tumhara kya injaam hoga )? aur iss jaisay aik kalaam par to bani Israel ka aik gawah shahadat bhi day chuka hai woh imaan le aaya aur tum apne ghamand mein parre rahay aisay zaalmon ko Allah hadaayat nahi diya karta """
  46,11,jin logon ne maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai woh imaan laane walon ke mutaliq kehte hain ke agar is kitaab ko maan lena koi acha kaam hota to yeh log is muamlay mein hum se Sabqat nah le ja satke thay chunkay unhon ne uss se hadaayat nah payi is liye ab yeh zaroor kahin ge ke yeh to purana jhoot hai
  46,12,"halaank iss se pehlay moose ki kitaab rehnuma aur rehmat ban kar aa chuki hai, aur yeh kitaab uss ki tasdeeq karne wali zabaan arabi mein aayi hai taakay zaalmon ko mutnabba kar day aur naik rawish ikhtiyar karne walon ko basharat day day"
  46,13,"yaqeenan jin logon ne keh diya ke Allah hi hamara rab hai, phir uss par jim gay, unn ke liye nah koi khauf hai aur nah woh ghamgeen hon ge"
  46,14,aisay sab log jannat mein jaane walay hain jahan woh hamesha rahen ge apne unn aamaal ke badlay jo woh duniya mein karte rahay hain
  46,15,"hum ne ensaan ko hadaayat ki ke woh apne walidain ke sath naik Bar tao kere uss ki maa ne mushaqqat utha kar usay pait mein rakha aur mushaqqat utha kar hi is ko jina, aur is ke hamal aur doodh chhuranay mein tees mahinay lag gay yahan taq ke jab woh apni poori taaqat ko pouncha aur chalees saal ka ho gaya to is ne kaha"" ae mere rab, mujhe tofeq day ke mein teri unn nematon ka shukar ada karoon jo to ne mujhe aur mere walidain ko ataa farmaen, aur aisa naik amal karoon jis se to raazi ho, aur meri aulaad ko bhi naik bana kar mujhe sُkh day, mein tairay huzoor tauba karta hon aur tabay farmaan ( muslim ) bundon mein se hon """
  46,16,iss terhan ke logon se hum unn ke behtareen aamaal ko qubool karte hain aur un ki buraiyon se dar guzar kar jatay hain yeh janati logon mein shaamil hon ge uss sachey waday ke mutabiq jo un se kya jata raha hai
  46,17,"aur jis shakhs ne apne walidain se kaha"" uff, tang kar diya tum ne, kya tum mujhe yeh khauf dilatey ho ke mein marnay ke baad phir qabar se nikala jaoon ga halaank mujh se pehlay bohat si naslen guzar chuki hain ( unn mein se to koi uth kar nah aaya )"" maa aur baap Allah ki dohai dey kar kehte hain"" arrey badnaseeb, maan ja, Allah ka wada sacha hai"" magar woh kehta hai"" yeh sab aglay waqton ki farsodah kahaniyan hain """
  46,18,yeh woh log hain jin par azaab ka faisla chaspan ho chuka hai inn se pehlay junoo aur insanon ke jo tolay ( isi qmash ke ) ho guzray hain aُnhi mein yeh bhi ja shaamil hon ge be shak yeh ghatay mein reh jaane walay log hain
  46,19,dono garohoon mein se har aik ke darjay un ke aamaal ke lehaaz se hain taakay Allah un ke kiye ka poora poora badla un ko day un par zulm hargiz nah kya jaye ga
  46,20,"phir jab yeh kafir aag ke samnay laa kharray kiye jayen ge to un se kaha jaye ga :"" tum apne hissay ki naematain apni duniya ki zindagi mein khatam kar chuke aur un ka lutaf tum ne utha liya, ab jo taqqabur tum zameen mein kisi haq ke baghair karte rahay aur jo nafarmaniyan tum ne kee unn ki Padaash mein aaj tum ko zillat ka azaab diya jaye ga """
  46,21,"zara aِnhin Aad ke bhai ( hood ) ka qissa sunaaoo jabkay uss ne احقاف mein apni qoum ko khabardaar kya tha aur aisay khabardaar karne walay uss se pehlay bhi guzar chuke thay aur is ke baad bhi atay rahay ke"" Allah ke siwa kisi ki bandagi nah karo, mujhe tumahray haq mein aik barray holnaak din ke azaab ka andesha hai """
  46,22,"unhon ne kaha"" kya to iss liye aaya hai ke hamein b_hka kar hamaray mabodon se bur-ghashta kar day? acha to le aa apna woh azaab jis se to hamein darata hai agar waqai to sacha hai """
  46,23,"uss ne kaha ke"" iss ka ilm to Allah ko hai, mein sirf woh pegham tumhe pouncha raha hon jisay day kar mujhe bheja gaya hai magar mein dekh raha hon ke tum log jahalat bart rahay ho """
  46,24,"phir jab unhon ne uss azaab ko apni vadyon ki taraf atay dekha to kehnay lagey"" yeh baadal hai jo hum ko sairaab kar day ga"" "" nahi, balkay yeh wohi cheez hai jis ke liye tum jaldi macha rahay thay yeh howa ka tufaan hai jis mein dard naak azaab chala aa raha hai"
  46,25,"apne rab ke hukum se har cheez ko tabah kar daaley ga"" aakhir kaar unn ka haal yeh howa ke unn ke rehne ki jaghon ke siwa wahan kuch nazar nah aata tha iss terhan hum mujrimon ko badla diya karte hain"
  46,26,"unn ko hum ne woh kuch diya tha jo tum logon ko nahi diya hai unn ko hum ne kaan, ankhen aur dil, sab kuch day rakhay thay, magar nah woh kaan unn ke kisi kaam aeye, nah ankhen, nah dil, kyunkay woh Allah ki ayaat ka inkaar karte thay, aur usi cheez ke phair mein woh aa gay jis ka woh mazaq uratay thay"
  46,27,"tumahray gird o paish ke ilaqon mein bohat si bustiyon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain hum ne apni ayaat bhaij kar baar baar terhan terhan se unn ko samjhaya, shayad ke woh baz aa jayen"
  46,28,"phir kyun nah unn hstyon ne unn ki madad ki jinhein Allah ko chore kar unhon ne taqarab eli Allah ka zareya samajte hue mabood bana liya tha? balkay woh to un se khoye gay, aur yeh tha unn ke jhoot aur unn banawati aqeedon ka injaam jo unhon ne ghurr rakhay thay"
  46,29,( aur woh waqea bhi qabil zikar hai ) jab hum junoo ke aik giroh ko tumhari taraf le aeye thay taakay quran sunen jab woh uss jagah puhanche ( jahan tum quran parh rahay thay ) to unhon ne aapas mein kaha khamosh ho jao phir jab woh parha ja chuka to woh khabardaar karne walay ban kar apni qoum ki taraf palty
  46,30,"unhon ne ja kar kaha,"" ae hamari qoum ke logo, hum ne aik kitaab suni hai jo moose ke baad nazil ki gayi hai, tasdeeq karne wali hai apne se pehlay aayi hui kitabon ki, rahnumai karti hai haq aur raah raast ki taraf"
  46,31,"ae hamari qoum ke logo, Allah ki taraf bulanay walay ki dawat qubool kar lau aur is par imaan le aao, Allah tumahray gunaaho se dar guzar farmaiye ga aur tumhe azaab alim se bacha day ga """
  46,32,"aur jo koi Allah ke Daiee ki baat nah manay woh nah zameen mein khud koi bil bota rakhta hai ke Allah ko zich kar day, aur nah is ke koi aisay haami o sarparast hain ke Allah se is ko bacha len aisay log khuli gumraahi mein par y hue hain"
  46,33,"aur kya inn logon ko yeh sujhai nahi deta ke jis khuda ne yeh zameen aur aasman peda kiye hain aur un ko banatay hue jo nah thaka, woh zaroor is par Qadir hai ke mُrdon ko jala uthaye? kyun nahi, yaqeenan woh har cheez ki qudrat rakhta hai"
  46,34,"jis roz yeh kafir aag ke samnay laaye jayen ge, uss waqt inn se poocha jaye ga"" kya yeh haq nahi hai ?"" yeh kahin ge"" haan, hamaray rab ki qasam ( yeh waqai haq hai )"" Allah farmaiye ga,"" acha to ab azaab ka maza chako apne uss inkaar ki Padaash mein jo tum karte rahay thay """
  46,35,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr karo jis terhan oalul azm Rasolo-n ne sabr kya hai, aur un ke maamla mein jaldi nah karo jis roz yeh log uss cheez ko dekh len ge jis ka aِnhin khauf dilaya ja raha hai to aِnhin yun maloom ho ga ke jaisay duniya mein din ki aik gharri bhar se ziyada nahi rahay thay baat pouncha di gayi, ab kya nafarman logon ke siwa aur koi halaak ho ga ?"
